  "body_html": "<div class=\"\"> <!--Title box--><div class=\"stm_titlebox stm_titlebox_style_2 stm_titlebox_text-center\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"stm_flex stm_flex_last stm_flex_center\"><div class=\"stm_titlebox__inner\"><h1 class=\"h1 stm_titlebox__title no_line text-transform stm_mgb_2\"> Quem somos</h1><div class=\"stm_titlebox__subtitle\"></div></div></div></div></div> <!--Breadcrumbs--><div class=\"stm_page_bc container\"><div class=\"stm_breadcrumbs heading-font\"><div class=\"container\"> <span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"ir para OFCONSULTORES.\" href=\"../../\" class=\"home\"><span property=\"name\">OFCONSULTORES</span></a><meta property=\"position\" content=\"1\"></span> &gt; <span property=\"itemListElement\" typeof=\"ListItem\"><a property=\"item\" typeof=\"WebPage\" title=\"Ir para OFCONSULTORES.\" href=\"../\" class=\"post post-page\"><span property=\"name\">OFCONSULTORES</span></a><meta property=\"position\" content=\"2\"></span> &gt; <span class=\"post post-page current-item\">Quem somos</span></div></div></div><div class=\"\"><div class=\"stm_markup stm_markup_full\"><div class=\"stm_markup__content\"><div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><div class=\"codeless-content\" data-codeless=\"true\"><div class=\"container vc_container   \"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h3 style=\"color: #148EA6;text-align: center\" class=\"vc_custom_heading text-transform vc_custom_1748527231936 text-uppercase   text-center\">uma empresa de Pessoas e para Pessoas</h3></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container vc_container   \"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1590532766532\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Somos uma empresa&nbsp;</span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">de</span></i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;Pessoas e&nbsp;</span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">para</span></i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;Pessoas que investe no desenvolvimento e capacitação do Capital Humano, desde 22 de maio de 1996.&nbsp; Acreditamos que as Pessoas têm um potencial infinito na expressão dos seus talentos, necessitando apenas de encontrar o contexto adequado e a força impulsionadora para fazer acontecer.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left  vc_custom_1590532588237\"><figure class=\"wpb_wrapper vc_figure stm_lightgallery\"> <a data-rel=\"prettyPhoto[rel-1895-2037543776]\" href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818-1024x759.jpg\" target=\"_self\" class=\"vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey stm_lightgallery__selector\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1240\" height=\"919\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201240%20919'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818.jpg\" class=\"vc_single_image-img attachment-full lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"GoogleDrive_20200208_150445\" data-srcset=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818.jpg 1240w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818-300x222.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818-1024x759.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_20200208_150445-scaled-e1590532572818-768x569.jpg 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"></a></figure></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Para nós, os profissionais são, muito mais do que recursos humanos, são a essência das empresas, o seu Capital de Valor acrescido. Por isso privilegiamos a expressão Capital Humano. </span></p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Investimos na descoberta e no desenvolvimento das&nbsp;</span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">soft</span></i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">skills</span></i><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;e hard&nbsp;</span></i><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">skills</span></i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;das Pessoas para que estas sejam felizes e acrescentem valor, competitividade e rentabilidade às Empresas.&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559731&quot;:284,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">O&nbsp;</span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">core business&nbsp;</span></i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">da</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;OFCONSULTORES é a Formação e Consultoria na Gestão do Capital Humano, promovendo uma simbiose entre o bem-estar da Pessoa e o seu Valor para a Organização.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559731&quot;:284,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}\">&nbsp;</span></p></div></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element vc_custom_1590532873189 pull-left\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p class=\"stm_mf stm_mgb_0 fwsb\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 22px;\">Odete Fachada</p><p><span class=\"stm_mf fwsb\" style=\"color: #222222; font-size: 12px;\">DIRETORA</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container vc_container  vc_custom_1590532917773 \"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><h4 style=\"text-align: center\" class=\"vc_custom_heading vc_custom_1590532903117   text-center\">Desde 2010 que:</h4></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container vc_container   \"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1748527699411 vc_row-o-equal-height vc_row-o-content-middle vc_row-flex\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner vc_custom_1590431154716\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Estamos presentes <strong>além-fronteiras</strong>, com especial relevância em Angola.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner vc_custom_1590429356241\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Temos <strong>parceiros de Excelência</strong> que confiam nos nossos projetos e modelos de atuação sendo, por isso, impulsionadores da sua sustentabilidade e do seu Sucesso.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner vc_custom_1748527616298\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Desenhamos <strong>Modelos de Liderança Estratégica</strong>, altamente impactantes e dinamizadores do potencial das Pessoas.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1590431106230 vc_row-o-equal-height vc_row-o-content-middle vc_row-flex\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner vc_custom_1590431154716\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Construímos e sistematizamos <strong>Modelos de Cultura Organizacional</strong> que refletem a forma de ser e de estar da Organização e da Empresa permitindo que se destaquem </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">no mercado</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;em que atuam.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559740&quot;:360}\">&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4 vc_col-has-fill\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner vc_custom_1590429356241\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_center\"><figure class=\"wpb_wrapper vc_figure stm_lightgallery\"><div class=\"vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey\"><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1580\" height=\"1561\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201580%201561'%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598.jpg\" class=\"vc_single_image-img attachment-full lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"GoogleDrive_3086\" data-srcset=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598.jpg 1580w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598-300x296.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598-1024x1012.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598-768x759.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2020/05/GoogleDrive_3086-scaled-e1590429926598-1536x1518.jpg 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 15